Package Model

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractQuestionDriver
    An abstract class for a component of the Game class that handles question choosing and switching.
    Constants
    Contains constants that play role of default values for some parameters in this package.
    Game
    The class that implements the finite automata, that is the base of game process.
    Player  
    PrimitiveSequentialQuestionDriver
    Primitive implementation of question driver.
    Question
    Represents question that is asked to players.
    Timer
    En entity for handling timeouts, based on ScheduledThreadPoolExecutor
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    GameException
    Classes of this object are thrown by methods of Game class (specifically if some method of Game object is called when Game object is in the state when this method can not be executed; in this case the message field of GameException.GameException(java.lang.String) object usually contents "Illegal game state").
